{"TopicId":219568,"ForumId":120,"TopicTitle":"Adjusting alternative sensitivity","CreatedByName":"cocoscacao","CreatedById":225696,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-09-20T11:27:54Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"cocoscacao","CreatedById":225696,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-09-20T11:27:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo caps lock is used to alternate input sensitivity. However, in most cases, the sensitivity of that input is too low (especially planes, rockets are good). It would be nice to have some slider for each vessel to adjust alternate sensitivity from 1% to 100%.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Mikki","CreatedById":137508,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-09-20T17:31:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI agree to the \u003Cabbr title=\u00221. Original Post(er). The first post in a thread, or the person who posted it. 2. Overpowered. A part or mechanic that upsets game balance by being too powerful.\u0022\u003EOP\u003C/abbr\u003E, i would also like to have simple autopilot functionality as \u0060Hold Level\u0060and \u0060\u0060Force Pitch/ Attidude\u0060 while piloting in atmosphere. Oh, and where is the reset trim button combo? Did i miss something here?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Stoup","CreatedById":2804,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-09-20T19:14:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI think it\u0027s still alt\u002Bx, but I have no idea how you\u0027d find that out from in-game\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Lyneira","CreatedById":149515,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-09-25T10:09:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224324023\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022219568\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221695231068\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022137508\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Mikki\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 9/20/2023 at 7:31 PM, Mikki said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI agree to the \u003Cabbr title=\u00221. Original Post(er). The first post in a thread, or the person who posted it. 2. Overpowered. A part or mechanic that upsets game balance by being too powerful.\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u00221. Original Post(er). The first post in a thread, or the person who posted it. 2. Overpowered. A part or mechanic that upsets game balance by being too powerful.\u0022\u003EOP\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E, i would also like to have simple autopilot functionality as \u0060Hold Level\u0060and \u0060\u0060Force Pitch/ Attidude\u0060 while piloting in atmosphere. Oh, and where is the reset trim button combo? Did i miss something here?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224324047\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022219568\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221695237282\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u00222804\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Stoup\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 9/20/2023 at 9:14 PM, Stoup said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI think it\u0027s still alt\u002Bx, but I have no idea how you\u0027d find that out from in-game\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlt-X does reset your trim. It also instantly sets your throttle to 0 because \u0022x\u0022 without modifiers is the key for that.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}